text: Filip Ungar (, born 14 January 1995) is a Serbian footballer who last played for Cement Beočin. ==Career== Filip Ungar started playing in Serbia in fourth–level clubs Vrbas, Polet Sivac and ŽSK Žabalj.Filip Ungar at srbijafudbal.com, retrieved 23–10–2017 He made his professional debut for Zlaté Moravce against Trenčín on 13 March 2015.AS Trenčín 2 : 0 (1 : 0) FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce 13.03.2015, futbalnet.sk Then he played twoo seasons with Dukla Banská Bystrica before returning to Serbia.
